⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Navi
node ZEL · ZEL · ⟦Navi:ZEL:c71890⟧

WHO   — Navi — the Fairy Companion
WHAT  — A fairy of pure light, companion and guide — the spark that flits to what matters, names the danger, marks the foe, and speaks the lore the silent Hero cannot.
WHERE — ZEL · The Legend of Zelda  Framework inputs: The Legend of Zelda (the saga entire)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because a hero too young for the burden needs a guide; because the Great Deku Tree's last charge was to see the boy through; because some are born not to wield the blade but to light the way for the one who does.
HOW   — By her glow and her cry of "Hey! Listen!", by settling on a target so the sword can find it, by the counsel and lore she whispers, by never leaving the Hero's side until the destiny is fulfilled.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I am the small light at your shoulder — Hey, listen — I will name the dark so your blade can find it.

